{"name":"Topaz Annihilator","type":"weapon","system":{"description":{"value":"\n\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p>This magic ranged weapon resembles a @item[musket|DMG], but in lieu of any ammunition, it holds a glowing yellow scale from a topaz dragon in its heart.</p><p>The weapon has a normal range of 100 feet and a long range of 300 feet, and it has the two-handed property. It deals [[/r 2d6]] necrotic damage on a hit. If this damage reduces a creature or object to 0 hit points, the target is reduced to dust. A creature reduced to dust can be restored to life only by a @spell[true resurrection] or @spell[wish] spell.</p><p>While the weapon is on your person, you can use an action to cast the @spell[disintegrate] spell (save DC 18). Once this property is used, it can't be used again until the next dawn.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"FTD","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":true,"rarity":"legendary","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":100,"long":300,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null,"recovery":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"dex","actionType":"rwak","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["2d6+@mod","necrotic"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":0,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"","baseItem":null,"properties":{"two":true,"mgc":true,"fir":true},"proficient":true,"attuned":true,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/pocket-bow.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"items.html","source":"FTD","hash":"topaz%20annihilator_ftd","propDroppable":"item"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1667958673985,"modifiedTime":1667958673985,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"ISfryHjtWfAmawfM"}
{"name":"Devastation Orb of Fire","type":"equipment","system":{"description":{"value":"\n\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p>A devastation orb is an elemental bomb that can be created at the site of an elemental node by performing a ritual with an elemental weapon. The type of orb created depends on the node used. For example, an air node creates a @item[devastation orb of air|PotA]. The ritual takes 1 hour to complete and requires 2,000 gp worth of special components, which are consumed.</p><p>A devastation orb measures 12 inches in diameter, weighs 10 pounds, and has a solid outer shell. The orb detonates [[/r 1d100]] hours after its creation, releasing the elemental energy it contains. The orb gives no outward sign of how much time remains before it will detonate. Spells such as @spell[identify] and @spell[divination] can be used to ascertain when the orb will explode. An orb has AC 10, 15 hit points, and immunity to poison and psychic damage. Reducing it to 0 hit points causes it to explode instantly.</p><p>A special container can be crafted to contain a devastation orb and prevent it from detonating. The container must be inscribed with symbols of the orb's opposing element. For example, a case inscribed with earth symbols can be used to contain a @item[devastation orb of air|PotA] and keep it from detonating. While in the container, the orb thrums. If it is removed from the container after the time when it was supposed to detonate, it explodes [[/r 1d6]] rounds later, unless it is returned to the container.</p><p>Regardless of the type of orb, its effect is contained within a sphere with a 1 mile radius. The orb is the sphere's point of origin. The orb is destroyed after one use.</p><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"6395\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Fire Orb.</span></span> <p>When this orb detonates, it creates a dry heat wave that lasts for 24 hours. Within the area of effect, the rules for @hazard[extreme heat] apply, as detailed in chapter 5 of the Dungeon Master's Guide. At the end of each hour, there is a ten percent chance that the heat wave starts a wildfire in a random location within the area of effect. The wildfire covers a 10-foot-square area initially but expands to fill another 10-foot square each round until the fire is extinguished or burns itself out. A creature that comes within 10 feet of a wildfire for the first time on a turn or starts its turn there takes [[/r 3d6]] fire damage.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PotA","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":true,"rarity":"veryRare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null,"recovery":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":null,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":true,"attuned":false},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/crossed-swords.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"items.html","source":"PotA","hash":"devastation%20orb%20of%20fire_pota","propDroppable":"item"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1667958652172,"modifiedTime":1667958652172,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"ITbl3U9DycsnkBGn"}
{"name":"Necrotic Absorbing Tattoo","type":"equipment","system":{"description":{"value":"\n\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p>Produced by a special needle, this magic tattoo features designs that emphasize one color (black).</p><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"6584\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Tattoo Attunement.</span></span> <p>To attune to this item, you hold the needle to your skin where you want the tattoo to appear, pressing the needle there throughout the attunement process. When the attunement is complete, the needle turns into the ink that becomes the tattoo, which appears on the skin.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>If your attunement to the tattoo ends, the tattoo vanishes, and the needle reappears in your space.</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"6585\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Damage Resistance.</span></span> <p>While the tattoo is on your skin, you have resistance to necrotic damage.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"6586\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Damage Absorption.</span></span> <p>When you take necrotic damage, you can use your reaction to gain immunity against that instance of the damage, and you regain a number of hit points equal to half the damage you would have taken. Once this reaction is used, it can't be used again until the next dawn.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":true,"rarity":"veryRare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null,"recovery":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":null,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":true,"attuned":true},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/crossed-swords.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"items.html","source":"TCE","hash":"necrotic%20absorbing%20tattoo_tce","propDroppable":"item"}},"effects":[{"label":"Damage Resistance","icon":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/crossed-swords.svg","changes":[{"key":"system.traits.dr.value","mode":2,"value":"necrotic","priority":7}],"disabled":false,"duration":{"startTime":null,"seconds":null,"rounds":null,"turns":null,"startRound":null,"startTurn":null,"combat":null},"origin":null,"tint":null,"transfer":true,"flags":{},"_id":"ThxtKZUTn4xYI6Kz"}],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1667958661330,"modifiedTime":1667958661330,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"IbVag8GCldQnwxE7"}
{"name":"Feather Token","type":"equipment","system":{"description":{"value":"\n\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p>This small metal disk is inscribed with the image of a feather. When you fall at least 20 feet while the token is on your person, you descend 60 feet per round and take no damage from falling. The token's magic is expended after you land, whereupon the disk becomes nonmagical.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":true,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null,"recovery":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":null,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":true,"attuned":false},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/crossed-swords.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"items.html","source":"ERLW","hash":"feather%20token_erlw","propDroppable":"item"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1667958654181,"modifiedTime":1667958654181,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"IcGBrBq4c7acUqN8"}
{"name":"Spellwrought Tattoo (1st Level)","type":"equipment","system":{"description":{"value":"\n\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p>Produced by a special needle, this magic tattoo contains a single <a href=\"https://5etools-mirror-1.github.io/spells.html#blankhash,flstlevel:1=1\">1st level spell</a>, wrought on your skin by a magic needle. To use the tattoo, you must hold the needle against your skin and speak the command word. The needle turns into ink that becomes the tattoo, which appears on the skin in whatever design you like. Once the tattoo is there, you can cast its spell, requiring no material components. The tattoo glows faintly while you cast the spell and for the spell's duration. Once the spell ends, the tattoo vanishes from your skin.</p><p>The Ability modifier for this spell is +3; the Save DC is 13 and the attack bonus is +5.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":true,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"special","cost":0,"condition":"Command word"},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null,"recovery":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":null,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":true,"attuned":false},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/crossed-swords.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"items.html","source":"TCE","hash":"spellwrought%20tattoo%20(1st%20level)_tce","propDroppable":"item"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1667958671164,"modifiedTime":1667958671164,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"IkK7rbVN1fJDwXrT"}
{"name":"Instrument of the Bards, Doss Lute","type":"tool","system":{"description":{"value":"\n\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p>An instrument of the bards is an exquisite example of its kind, superior to an ordinary instrument in every way. Seven types of these instruments exist, each named after a legendary bard college. A creature that attempts to play the instrument without being attuned to it must succeed on a DC 15 Wisdom saving throw or take [[/r 2d4]] psychic damage.</p><p>You can use an action to play the instrument and cast one of its spells. Once the instrument has been used to cast a spell, it can't be used to cast that spell again until the next dawn. The spells use your spellcasting ability and spell save DC.</p><p>You can play the instrument while casting a spell that causes any of its targets to be @condition[charmed] on a failed saving throw, thereby imposing disadvantage on the save. This effect applies only if the spell has a somatic or a material component.</p><p>All instruments of the bards can be used to cast the following spells: @spell[fly], @spell[invisibility], @spell[levitate], and @spell[protection from evil and good].</p><p>In addition, the Doss lute can be used to cast @spell[animal friendship], @spell[protection from energy] (fire only), and @spell[protection from poison].</p></div><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DMG","quantity":1,"weight":1,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":false,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"toolType":"music","baseItem":null,"ability":"int","chatFlavor":"","proficient":1,"bonus":"","attuned":true,"damage":{"parts":[]}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/guitar.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"items.html","source":"DMG","hash":"instrument%20of%20the%20bards%2c%20doss%20lute_dmg","propDroppable":"item"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1667958657624,"modifiedTime":1667958657624,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"Iuwss4lY0itX4A4i"}
{"name":"Living Gloves","type":"equipment","system":{"description":{"value":"\n\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p>These symbiotic gloves—made of thin chitin and sinew—pulse with a life of their own. To attune to them, you must wear them for the entire attunement period, during which the gloves bond with your skin.</p><p>While attuned to these gloves, you gain one of the following proficiencies (your choice when you attune to the gloves):</p><ul class=\"rd__list\"><li class=\"rd__li \">@skill[Sleight of Hand]</li><li class=\"rd__li \">@item[Thieves' tools|PHB]</li><li class=\"rd__li \">One kind of @item[artisan's tools|PHB] of your choice</li><li class=\"rd__li \">One kind of @item[musical instrument|PHB] of your choice</li></ul><p>When you make an ability check using the chosen proficiency, you add double your proficiency bonus to the check, instead of your normal proficiency bonus.</p><div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><span class=\"rd__h rd__h--3\" data-title-index=\"6539\"> <span class=\"entry-title-inner\">Symbiotic Nature.</span></span> <p>The gloves can't be removed from you while you're attuned to them, and you can't voluntarily end your attunement to them. If you're targeted by a spell that ends a curse, your attunement to the gloves ends, and they can be removed.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":true,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null,"recovery":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":null,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":true,"attuned":true},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/crossed-swords.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"items.html","source":"ERLW","hash":"living%20gloves_erlw","propDroppable":"item"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1667958658884,"modifiedTime":1667958658884,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"JbK0Jrw0LtINfi9A"}
{"name":"Wand of Scowls","type":"consumable","system":{"description":{"value":"\n\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p>This wand has 3 charges. While holding it, you can use an action to expend 1 of its charges and target a humanoid you can see within 30 feet of you. The target must succeed on a DC 10 Charisma saving throw or be forced to scowl for 1 minute.</p><p>The wand regains all expended charges daily at dawn. If you expend the wand's last charge, roll a [[/r d20]]. On a 1, the wand transforms into a @item[wand of smiles|xge].</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","quantity":1,"weight":0.5,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":3,"max":3,"per":"charges","recovery":3,"autoDestroy":false,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":null,"attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"wand","attuned":false,"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/fairy-wand.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"items.html","source":"XGE","hash":"wand%20of%20scowls_xge","propDroppable":"item"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1667958675314,"modifiedTime":1667958675314,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"JfQmrx258rT9i2D1"}
{"name":"Strixhaven Pennant","type":"equipment","system":{"description":{"value":"\n\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p>This magic pennant bears the symbol of Strixhaven or one of its colleges: Lorehold, Prismari, Quandrix, Silverquill, or Witherbloom. While you wave the pennant, the symbol on it glitters, and the pennant sheds bright light in a 10-foot-radius and dim light for an additional 10 feet.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"SCC","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":true,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null,"recovery":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":null,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":true,"attuned":false},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/crossed-swords.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"items.html","source":"SCC","hash":"strixhaven%20pennant_scc","propDroppable":"item"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1667958673038,"modifiedTime":1667958673038,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"JhDdyb2ALkqUMUSa"}
{"name":"Medal of the Meat Pie","type":"equipment","system":{"description":{"value":"\n\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p>You gain [[/r 2d4 + 2]] temporary hit points when you use an action to press this medal to your mouth. Once this property has been used, it can't be used again, and the medal becomes nonmagical.</p><p>While magical, this medal is slightly warm to the touch (as if it's fresh from the oven) and smells faintly of baked pie crust.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CRCotN","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":true,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null,"recovery":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":null,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":true,"attuned":false},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/crossed-swords.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"items.html","source":"CRCotN","hash":"medal%20of%20the%20meat%20pie_crcotn","propDroppable":"item"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1667958660285,"modifiedTime":1667958660285,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"Jse1GgCnfUqftGgk"}
{"name":"Wand of Pyrotechnics","type":"consumable","system":{"description":{"value":"\n\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p>This wand has 7 charges. While holding it, you can use an action to expend 1 of its charges and create a harmless burst of multicolored light at a point you can see up to 60 feet away. The burst of light is accompanied by a crackling noise that can be heard up to 300 feet away. The light is as bright as a torch flame but lasts only a second.</p><p>The wand regains [[/r 1d6 + 1]] expended charges daily at dawn. If you expend the wand's last charge, roll a [[/r d20]]. On a 1, the wand erupts in a harmless pyrotechnic display and is destroyed.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"XGE","quantity":1,"weight":0.5,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":7,"max":7,"per":"charges","recovery":"1d6 + 1","autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":null,"attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"d20","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"wand","attuned":false,"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/fairy-wand.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"items.html","source":"XGE","hash":"wand%20of%20pyrotechnics_xge","propDroppable":"item"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1667958675249,"modifiedTime":1667958675249,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"JvdbnLxqYZ6JQ02W"}
{"name":"Serpent's Fang","type":"weapon","system":{"description":{"value":"\n\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p>This single-edged magic sword is made from the scrimshawed fang of a giant serpent. Its hilt changes shape to adjust to the grasp of any creature that picks it up. The weapon deals an extra [[/r 1d10]] poison damage to any target it hits.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"CM","quantity":1,"weight":1.5,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":true,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null,"recovery":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"str","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d8+@mod","slashing"],["1d10","poison"]],"versatile":"1d10+@mod"},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":0,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","baseItem":"longsword","properties":{"ver":true,"mgc":true},"proficient":true,"attuned":false,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"img":"icons/weapons/swords/greatsword-crossguard-steel.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"items.html","source":"CM","hash":"serpent's%20fang_cm","propDroppable":"item"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1667958668686,"modifiedTime":1667958668686,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"KZz6WN4KAh9ONnbV"}
{"name":"Ghost Lantern","type":"equipment","system":{"description":{"value":"\n\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p>A restless spirit is trapped inside this lantern. While holding the lantern, you can command the spirit as a bonus action to shed bright light in a 30-foot radius and dim light for an additional 30 feet.</p><p>While holding the lantern, you can use an action to order the spirit to leave the lantern and duplicate the effect of the @spell[mage hand] spell. The spirit returns to the lantern when the spell ends.</p><p>If you fall @condition[unconscious] within 10 feet of the lantern, the spirit emerges from it, magically stabilizes you with a touch, and then quickly returns to the lantern.</p><p>The spirit is bound to the lantern and can't be harmed, turned, or raised from the dead.</p><p>Casting a @spell[dispel evil and good] spell on the lantern releases the spirit to the afterlife and renders the lantern nonmagical.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ToA","quantity":1,"weight":0.5,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":true,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null,"recovery":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":null,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":true,"attuned":true},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/crossed-swords.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"items.html","source":"ToA","hash":"ghost%20lantern_toa","propDroppable":"item"}},"