{"name":"Saddle of the Cavalier","type":"equipment","system":{"description":{"value":"\n\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p>While in this saddle on a mount, you can't be dismounted against your will if you're conscious, and attack rolls against the mount have disadvantage.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DMG","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":true,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null,"recovery":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":null,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":true,"attuned":false},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/crossed-swords.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"items.html","source":"DMG","hash":"saddle%20of%20the%20cavalier_dmg","propDroppable":"item"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1667958667555,"modifiedTime":1667958667555,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"yvm8JBSkgvw5weaV"}
{"name":"Cleansing Stone","type":"equipment","system":{"description":{"value":"\n\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p>A <i>cleansing stone</i> is a sphere 1 foot in diameter, engraved with mystic sigils. When touching the stone, you can use an action to activate it and remove dirt and grime from your garments and your person.</p><p>Such stones are often embedded in pedestals in public squares in Aundair or in high-end Ghallanda inns.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ERLW","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":true,"rarity":"common","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null,"recovery":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":null,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":true,"attuned":false},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/crossed-swords.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"items.html","source":"ERLW","hash":"cleansing%20stone_erlw","propDroppable":"item"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1667958650251,"modifiedTime":1667958650251,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"ywkrP62s0XAtNkXp"}
{"name":"Zevellon's Grasp","type":"equipment","system":{"description":{"value":"\n\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p>These gauntlets are warm to the touch. In their illusory form, they appear shiny, gold, and sturdy. In their true form, the fiery gauntlets are tipped with claws.</p><p>While you wear both gauntlets and have at least one free hand, you can use a bonus action to create a sword of green flame. While the sword is active, tiny screams sound in the crackling of the fire.</p><p>The sword is a one-handed melee weapon that deals [[/r 4d6]] damage on a hit. Each time you create the sword, you decide if it deals fire or necrotic damage. This weapon is dismissed if you are knocked @condition[unconscious] or when you use a bonus action to dispel it. You can't let go of the sword until you dismiss it. You can only have one sword at a time.</p><p>When you hit a creature with a melee weapon attack while wearing the gauntlets and you don't have a flame sword active, you can choose to deal an extra [[/r 2d6]] fire damage.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"Ar6","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":true,"rarity":"legendary","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null,"recovery":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":null,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":true,"attuned":true},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/crossed-swords.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"items.html","source":"Ar6","hash":"zevellon's%20grasp_ar6","propDroppable":"item"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1667958678413,"modifiedTime":1667958678413,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"yy9bhcmeE6O8zuHU"}
{"name":"Scroll of Protection from Fey","type":"consumable","system":{"description":{"value":"\n\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p>Using an action to read the scroll encloses you in an @condition[invisible] barrier that extends from you to form a 5-foot-radius, 10-foot-high cylinder. For 5 minutes, this barrier prevents fey from entering or affecting anything within the cylinder. The cylinder moves with you and remains centered on you. However, if you move in such a way that a fey would be inside the cylinder, the effect ends. A creature can attempt to overcome the barrier by using an action to make a DC 15 Charisma check. On a success, the creature ceases to be affected by the barrier.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"DMG","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":false,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null,"recovery":null,"autoDestroy":true,"autoUse":true},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":null,"attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"consumableType":"scroll","attuned":false,"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/tied-scroll.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"items.html","source":"DMG","hash":"scroll%20of%20protection%20from%20fey_dmg","propDroppable":"item"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1667958667966,"modifiedTime":1667958667966,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"yys1iDosecJIJqtQ"}
{"name":"Shield of Shouting","type":"equipment","system":{"description":{"value":"\n\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p>A @spell[detect magic] spell reveals an aura of transmutation magic around this shield, which has a minor magical property: words spoken by the shield's bearer are amplified and sound ten times louder than normal.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"ToA","quantity":1,"weight":3,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":true,"rarity":"","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null,"recovery":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":2,"type":"shield","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":null,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":true,"attuned":false},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/checked-shield.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"items.html","source":"ToA","hash":"shield%20of%20shouting_toa","propDroppable":"item"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1667958669014,"modifiedTime":1667958669014,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"z1MhHsdjj3AZmtCB"}
{"name":"Balloon Pack","type":"equipment","system":{"description":{"value":"\n\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p>This backpack contains the spirit of an @creature[air elemental] and a compact leather balloon. While you're wearing the backpack, you can deploy the balloon as an action and gain the effect of the @spell[levitate] spell for 10 minutes, targeting yourself and requiring no concentration. Alternatively, you can use a reaction to deploy the balloon when you're falling and gain the effect of the @spell[feather fall] spell for yourself.</p><p>When either spell ends, the balloon slowly deflates as the elemental spirit escapes and returns to the Elemental Plane of Air. As the balloon deflates, you descend gently toward the ground for up to 60 feet. If you are still in the air at the end of this distance, you fall if you have no other means of staying aloft.</p><p>After the spirit departs, the backpack's property is unusable unless the backpack is recharged for 1 hour in an elemental air node, which binds another spirit to the backpack.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"PotA","quantity":1,"weight":0,"price":null,"attunement":0,"equipped":true,"rarity":"uncommon","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"","cost":0,"condition":""},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":null,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":null,"long":null,"units":""},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null,"recovery":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":null,"amount":null},"ability":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":null,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":null,"type":"trinket","dex":null},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"baseItem":null,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""},"strength":null,"stealth":false,"proficient":true,"attuned":false},"img":"modules/plutonium/media/icon/crossed-swords.svg","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"items.html","source":"PotA","hash":"balloon%20pack_pota","propDroppable":"item"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1667958647847,"modifiedTime":1667958647847,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h":3},"_id":"z4vd1J89MjzNYZjh"}
{"name":"Devotee's Censer","type":"weapon","system":{"description":{"value":"\n\t\t<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--2\"><p>The rounded head of this flail is perforated with tiny holes, arranged in symbols and patterns. The flail counts as a holy symbol for you. When you hit with an attack using this magic flail, the target takes an extra [[/r 1d8]] radiant damage.</p><p>As a bonus action, you can speak the command word to cause the flail to emanate a thin cloud of incense out to 10 feet for 1 minute. At the start of each of your turns, you and any other creatures in the incense each regain [[/r 1d4]] hit points. This property can't be used again until the next dawn.</p></div>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"TCE","quantity":1,"weight":1,"price":null,"attunement":1,"equipped":true,"rarity":"rare","identified":true,"activation":{"type":"action","cost":1,"condition":"Command word"},"duration":{"value":0,"units":""},"target":{"value":0,"width":null,"units":"","type":""},"range":{"value":5,"long":0,"units":"ft"},"uses":{"value":null,"max":null,"per":null,"recovery":null},"consume":{"type":"","target":"","amount":null},"ability":"str","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":null,"chatFlavor":"","critical":{"threshold":null,"damage":""},"damage":{"parts":[["1d8+@mod","bludgeoning"],["1d8","radiant"]],"versatile":""},"formula":"","save":{"ability":"","dc":0,"scaling":"spell"},"armor":{"value":10},"hp":{"value":0,"max":0,"dt":null,"conditions":""},"weaponType":"martialM","baseItem":"flail","properties":{"mgc":true},"proficient":true,"attuned":true,"speed":{"value":null,"conditions":""}},"img":"icons/weapons/maces/mace-round-spiked-black.webp","flags":{"plutonium":{"page":"items.html","source":"TCE","hash":"devotee's%20censer_tce","propDroppable":"item"}},"effects":[],"_stats":{"systemId":"dnd5e","systemVersion":"2.0.3","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1667958652319,"modifiedTime":1667958652319,"lastModifiedBy":"pjd4PUp7eb3ERd0h"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":